Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:27.87,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}迴盪的鐘聲  與你的一點一滴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.87,0:22:32.11,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}願明日有個好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.11,0:22:36.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}能夠抵達星星那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:43.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}漫步在夜空下  望見一絲光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.19,0:22:48.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在月亮上面  即便孤獨一人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.27,0:22:55.88,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也要全力奔向螺旋的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:23:02.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你曾說哭過之後會再次歡笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:08.11,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那請不要忘記我們所走過的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:13.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}施展封印的魔法  不再去傳播離別
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:20.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}等到時機成熟  再邁出前進的腳步
Comment: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------EP.PartA--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介他回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個時刻終於到來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下…來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能停得下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為回來了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介他！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了啦  快點阻止那兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀  是理樹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  昨晚一夜沒睡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們倆在你回來之前可是忍好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為的就是等你回來仲裁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  就來定個規則好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空手的話  真人太強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反之拿著竹刀的話  謙吾就厲害過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都好啦  你們能隨便找點東西扔過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是沒什麼用的東西越好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以從中抓到的東西來當武器去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是些沒用處的小玩意  應該比現在安全多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Battle  Start
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香蕉？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為啥會捧著一隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的武器  有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  這該怎麼去打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的鈴大人駕到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以欺負弱小！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱小？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:02:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是說你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  不是說你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說這隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們打架的原因是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙故意教我「茅廁頓開」這句錯的成語
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜他所賜  今天在和別人說話的時候不經意說出一句
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「那還真是茅廁頓開啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相當雞毛蒜皮的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你先來問我「茅廁頓開」是什麼意思的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你是在問「茅塞頓開」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是回答說是突然一下子醒悟過來的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你開始就該這麼說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「茅廁頓開」是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  這下就明白誰是誰非了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛  想溜是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我用貓把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然動手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別以為是恭介的妹妹我就會手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們扔點武器進來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鰻  鰻魚派！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井之原同學  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的情景並不是今天才有的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從童年時與他們相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並與他們結伴而行以來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這便成了不斷重複的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個最難受的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母剛剛去世的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在憂鬱自閉的我面前出現了四個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強敵出現了  我們需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我們走  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懲惡揚善的正義夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人稱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little  Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無疑問是強敵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們奮勇地戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜂蜜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人  我們絕不會忘記你的犧牲！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這和說好的不一樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我們的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是宛如祭典般的時光的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他們在一起的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺中  讓我忘記了心中的痛楚與寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在享受著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中祈求這樣的時光能永遠持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪波奇  讓我吃了不少苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不叫波奇  新來的還沒有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫列儂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列儂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你起的名字總是這麼隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛因斯坦  蓋茲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧黛麗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了恭介  這次上哪裡找工作去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出版社  在東京的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步行去了東京？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錢嘛  有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們明年也將成為三年生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定會這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不會像你一樣步行去找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年後我們也得準備考試或者找工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到現在為止一直都在一起的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢業後也要各奔東西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少恭介一年後就不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不想去考慮啊  今後的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是現在能一直持續下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不像過去一樣  大家一起來做點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然間想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  我們小學時不是經常一起在附近巡邏尋找壞蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把我和你們混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介是領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總會為我們想出一些新奇好玩的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就來做點只有現在才能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來打棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打棒球啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來組建一支棒球隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊名就叫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little  Busters！
Comment: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------EP.PartB--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就站在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  你來做投手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且聽一下理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這種情節會比較燃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情節是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們Little  Busters參加的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是充滿了傳奇及感動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是受了漫畫的影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹  捕手就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  值得紀念的第一球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個作為開球式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要扔出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  用盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用盡全力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就直說了吧  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,授予你「神一般的高射炮」這個稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:19.55,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(320,332,320,325,0,1300)\fad(1600,0)}鈴獲得了稱號『神一般的高射炮』！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們Little  Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫且把這個房間當作活動室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒球部似乎發生了點情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上跟廢部沒什麼兩樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  為什麼是棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我升上了三年級
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在為找工作而四處奔波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然想到  自己到底在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會成為上班族  然後一直工作下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那只是一種追隨大潮的表現罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:12:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  我必須要證明我存在於這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  明明到中間還能聽明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最後的那句話完全不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為了證明自己還是自己而打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡為什麼會突然冒出個棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你試著想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙著找工作的時候居然還想打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會有這樣的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般不會有這樣的想法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為如此才有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是給牽連進來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就要比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為副將  我肩負著我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會為了證明自己還是自己而揮劍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謙吾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管他  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙總有一天  會理解我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個  我們也還完全沒能理解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1853年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,培理率艦隊駛進浦賀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1860年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星人來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1862年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  你不用做作業的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是在做著的嗎  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過話說回來  居然是棒球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  完全沒有料到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介他就愛做這種出乎人意料的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少這點要預料到的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  又來邀請我們打棒球了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是碰到了個麻煩的作業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要收集偉人們說過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偉人的話  是指名言嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓失前蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是名言是諺語啊  而且還錯得很離譜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這句話我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此時此刻  一句嶄新的名言誕生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:05.74,Sentence,NTP,0,0,0,,{\clip(268,73,268,107)}{\pos(320,105)\blur3\fad(0,1500)\t(0,250,1,\clip(268,73,370,107))}貓失前蹄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:05.74,Sentence,NTP,0,0,0,,{\clip(369,220,369,252)}{\pos(435,250)\blur3\fad(0,1500)\t(0,420,1,\clip(369,220,499,252))}井之原 真人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼非要把我給叫來男生宿舍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一樣  沒有幫人做作業的閒工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話  我就真的說出些名言來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「哇  這孩子也挺有能耐的」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們不禁發出這樣的感嘆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這句話我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:30.68,Sentence,NTP,0,0,0,,{\clip(235,77,235,112)}{\fad(0,1500)\blur3\an8\pos(320,83)\t(248,650,1,\clip(235,77,394,112))}這傢伙是笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:30.68,Sentence,NTP,0,0,0,,{\clip(193,211,193,246)}{\pos(398,242)\blur3\t(0,1330,0.8,\clip(193,211,591,246)\fad(0,1500)}棗 鈴{\fscy75\fscx75}（在仰望舊友·井之原真人時）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把說話時的場景也記錄下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅用了一句話就概括出真人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  嚓  噍嘰！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有一句意味深遠的名言誕生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:54.50,Sentence,NTP,0,0,0,,{\clip(247,64,247,96)}{\pos(320,96)\blur3\t(0,340,1,\clip(247,64,381,96))\fad(0,1500)}嘛  嚓  噍嘰！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:54.50,Sentence,NTP,0,0,0,,{\clip(295,227,295,282)}{\fs24\pos(398,282)\blur3\t(0,600,1,\clip(295,227,502,282))\fad(0,1500)}井之原真人\N（在回顧自己一生時）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的人生裡到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無非是一些亂七八糟的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是被你這傢伙給刺到了腰而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  棒球比賽的日程也定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little  Busters的第一場比賽近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了  恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要參加比賽我們缺了不少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的隊員和練習的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有除你之外的人的幹勁以及剩下的隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙說了兩次剩下的隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人這樣說有他自己的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要過分追究了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼意圖的  真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心我摸你把笨蛋傳染給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的隊員接下來去找就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打棒球的話  最少也要九個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能找到剩下的五個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說剩下五個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說謙吾沒被算進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  召集隊員的任務就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集隊員？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅長和陌生人說話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳機？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行動  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集其餘的五人就是你的任務！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把鈴放去女生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邀請女生們加入Little  Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是女生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要全是男人的話  那得多悶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是鈴  已潛入女生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的女生好像在下午也會說「早上好」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「早上好」太長了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡應該像個行家般  說個「早」就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼行家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我注意到個很要命的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們用很快的語速讀一下「Oliver  Sauce」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是聽著很像「早上好」？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…怎麼像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oliver  Sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:16:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任務失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那「俺是齊藤」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是聽著很像「早上好」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺是齊藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像極了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那鈴  你自己想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是齊藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？  我不是齊藤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是鈴  任務失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  直接說「晚上好」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  行動  邀請她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有興趣打棒球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗同學很有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說你有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗同學  這是什麼新遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對棒球有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這人…難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會忘了本小姐笹瀨川佐佐美是壘球部的下屆隊長候補吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說你是校內人氣居首的棗恭介同學的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與劍道部的英雄宮澤同學以及肌肉笨蛋關係很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}但也太囂張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉笨蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後你是英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很恰當不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  快和她說宮澤平時總會穿著衣服頭戴襪子去泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要  呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然說本小姐是呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨…笨蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們  給我上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}太囂張了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是佐佐美大人  太華麗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知從何時開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們總是被恭介的歪點子牽著鼻子走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至於他本人  和往常一樣在聚精會神地看著漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他所流露出的那份神聖的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至會讓其他班的女生趕過來欣賞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡笑  憤怒  時而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與少年時代毫無兩樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依舊是那麼地吸引人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到現在為止一直都在一起的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢業後也要各奔東西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少恭介一年後就不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就來做點只有現在才能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不禁也想邀請其他人加入Little  Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為最先提出想和大家一起做點什麼的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去打聲招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請…請問
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世上奇妙之事實在太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從天上掉下來了好多好多的糖果和點心
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------Next--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹  來打棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊名就叫  Little  Busters！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介  果然要說這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集隊員去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會懷著一顆熾熱的心等你好消息的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mission  Start！
